Module eu.lilithmonodia.winestock

Package eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data

@Deprecated(forRemoval=true) package eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data
Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
This package is deprecated and should not be used in new code.
The `eu.lilithmonodia.winestock.data` package is a collection of classes for handling data in the CSV (Comma Separated Value) format. These classes provide functionalities for reading CSV files and converting them into usable data structures or objects within the application. This package is deprecated, which means it's not recommended to use it in new code. Newer or more efficient alternatives should be considered for handling CSV data.
